name: Dabb Doge
description: Dabb Doge is a decentralized peer-to-peer digital currency that enables instant transactions to anyone anywhere in the world without any transaction fees. Dabb Doge has joined few NGO,s to help the stray dogs either who had an accident or are left stranded by their owner. Team has been able to rescue 487 Dogs, which gave birth to 176 puppies. We wish to continue on this path and help dogs as they can not speak for themselves so someone has to do stand for them and provide care in any way possible.
